1º Compañía de Comandos &quot;Iquique&quot;
The 1st Commandos Company "Iquique" ("1º Compañía de Comandos "Iquique"" in Spanish) is special forces unit under the jurisdiction of northern Chile. The unit is part of the 2nd Armored Brigade "Cazadores" ("2º Brigada Acorzada "Cazadores"" in Spanish) of the Sixth Army Division based in the first region of the country.
